    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Districts of cities in which members of a minority racial or cultural group live, especially because of social, legal, and economic pressure.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
